data.description: This is your chance to own a charming remodeled home for under $250k!  At the heart of the home is the stunning kitchen with grey cabinets, quartz countertops, shiplap backsplash and a elegant champagne bronze faucet.  Enjoy luxury vinyl plank flooring through out the house that is highly durable and waterproof.   Significant updates have been made to enhance comfort and convenience, including new windows, plumbing, and air conditioning systems, all upgraded between 2021 and 2022. Outside, the property features a sizable storage shed, providing ample space for your needs. Additionally, this home sits on two lots, offering generous room for outdoor activities or future expansion. This residence is not just a house, but a blend of modernity, style, and comfort, ready to be called home.
